PrecisAppointment of Wilfrid-Guy Licari as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Senegal; Verona Edelstein as High Commissioner for Canada to the United Republic of Tanzania; Christine Desloges as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Socialist Republic of Viet Nam; D. Martin Collacott as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Cambodia; Stanley Gooch as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of India concurrently accredited as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Nepal; Alain Dudoit as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Czech Republic; and Manfred G. von Nostitz as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary to the Kingdom of Thailand concurrently accredited as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the People's Democratic Republic of Laos.
